==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Epistler
<hw>E*pis"tler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
writer of epistles, or of an epistle of the New Testament.</def>
<rj><au>M. Arnold.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>The ecclesiastic who reads the
epistle at the communion service.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Epistolar</ent>⟦br⟧
